The paper discusses breakthrough discoveries and inventions in science and technology, and uses data from research papers and patents to construct models that predict next year's content and context combinations. This suggests a focus on machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.DL, cs.AI, cs.LG), as well as information retrieval (cs.IR) and social networks (cs.SI) which are relevant for analyzing the diverse contexts in which breakthroughs occur.
